wobani.toolbox.parameter

Class ParameterKey<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • wobani.toolbox.parameter.ParameterKey<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Parameter's generic type

    public class ParameterKey<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The key of a Parameter. It consists of two parts: the key and the return type. This two identifies a Parameter, not only the String key. The return type makes the ParameterContainer type safe.
